sub_title: Managing director at Edicated - EDI expert
summary:
Contact me at kevin@edicated.com

After a master degree from the Paris Sud XI university in IT technologies and 5 years working in North America as an EDI implementation engineer I started my own EDI consulting business in the Netherlands. Edicated is a dutch company offering consulting and IT services worldwide, we specialize in EDI implementation and blockchain technologies.
